---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Agentforce Vibes">
  <section class="about">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about__content">
        <h1 class="about__title">About Agentforce Vibes</h1>
        
        <div class="about__body">
          <p>
            Welcome to Agentforce Vibes, a blog dedicated to exploring the rapidly evolving world of AI agents, 
            automation, and enterprise technology transformation.
          </p>
          
          <p>
            AI is triggering the most profound organizational transformation since factories and the internet 
            rewired work. This revolution is much bigger than any single AI tool. It's a complete system, 
            and it's shifting power, culture, and decision-making across every level of the enterprise.
          </p>
          
          <p>
            Here, we explore what it means to build an <strong>agentic enterprise</strong> â€” where AI agents 
            work alongside humans, hierarchies flatten, silos break down, and entirely new forms of 
            collaboration emerge between humans and technology.
          </p>
          
          <h2>What We Cover</h2>
          
          <p>
            Our articles dive deep into topics like:
          </p>
          
          <ul>
            <li>Agentic AI and autonomous systems</li>
            <li>Enterprise transformation strategies</li>
            <li>Human-AI collaboration patterns</li>
            <li>Practical implementation guides</li>
            <li>Industry trends and insights</li>
            <li>Best practices for AI adoption</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
          
          <p>
            Have questions, feedback, or ideas for topics you'd like us to cover? We'd love to hear from you. 
            Reach out to us on social media or drop us a line.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: var(--space-16) 0 var(--space-20);
  }
  
  .about__content {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .about__title {
    font-size: var(--text-5xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .about__body h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    margin-top: var(--space-10);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }
  
  .about__body p {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }
  
  .about__body ul {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    padding-left: var(--space-8);
  }
  
  .about__body li {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }
  
  .about__body strong {
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }
</style>
